Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 发生了什么伤心事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭 我不希望你像乙姬那样难过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直陪在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就在这片海域 等待应答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就发着求救信号在这一带野外生存吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话 这边还有伤员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持距离进行搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通信 代码1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:00:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对照 龙宫岛高速机3架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离第一护盾 距离100
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALVIS 开始准备辅助着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助准备 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎减弱 维持常速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚瑠岛准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner驾驶员 到达机库
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门无反应 没有敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备解除护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除伪装镜面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到岛 能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能泡个热水澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了吗 奥尔加小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你·在·那·里·吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 侵入内心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断通信 快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵切换至副驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要活着…回去
