Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是…好担心小广
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点信心吧 小舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴牺牲性命传来了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把他带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快干活 镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在哪是办祭典的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种时候才要办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要化悲痛为力量 加深信赖与团结…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 里奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎么这么爱犯困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天牺牲了4人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 还有1人…可能是广登
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了那样的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有确定 不要告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈惠 那件事的回复我已告知镝木了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是需要那个计划的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人真面目未明 那样只会造成牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心解明真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次L计划若实现 生还者为零
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗力减半 岛会遭遇敌人袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12月17日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有这之后的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我们的终点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马广登特别篇 追寻神秘巨大生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning 龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:14:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们来追寻栖息在龙宫岛上的神秘生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}担任助手的是本岛的生物迷少女 立上芹…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傻 广登快回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为你准备的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一下子就会同化掉 觉得浪费…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会被同化 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没尝过食物的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师们都在担心我的健康
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我要是受伤或生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会将周围的生命都同化来保命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何生命 都是剥夺其他生命而活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了驾驶Fafner时以外都要孤单一人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想出去走走 看看蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 只要和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说要办祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去的话就和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会抑止你的同化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还需要你继续保护岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都只看见恶梦般的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请岛的核指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要我做些什么 为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是我给予了你们力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的存在催生了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像是我招来了不祥的未来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光看是不行的 要与未来抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择吧 选择生命的用途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一骑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与未来…抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的…用途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘无问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是启动实验而已吧 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 别担心 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次觉得Fafner好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对数螺旋形成 启动无问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,访问未来记录
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你·在·那·里·吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿哪件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香？浴衣自己能穿好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题…我不去祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有血腥味 没有血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗 来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去跟真壁司令和近藤医生说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话 这很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔加小姐 就死在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身是血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…也想变成那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 好好听妈的话就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈才应该听听我的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的盆舞也有若干变动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许跟我顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去姐姐那里的话 就自己一个人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把整个岛都卷进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连敌人在哪都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L计划什么的太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们究竟是为何而战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我也应该去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却只有姐姐去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是机会 早苗在呼唤我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会？呼唤好不容易幸存下来的家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要把我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把战死的人们都当傻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要舍弃别人让给我们的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家牺牲到底是为了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镝木之所以努力战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为…有你们…在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何数据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么一片空白地过了一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 时间并没过那么久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶时间和记录时间不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这不是数据错误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是机体内外的时间流速不一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示最新文档
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 在未来战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会更新其之前的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点在发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正应该改变的未来 必须打倒的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体内经过了两小时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边明明只过了一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中断启动实验
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除连接 把驾驶舱从机体内取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了什么 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白机体的力量了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体…是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的时间无法倒转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望永远都只存在于未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终将得知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追求未来 只能消耗生存于现在的生命
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------EDCN1---------------------------
