Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:10.35,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\blur2\fad(200,200)}蜷身抱住双膝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:15.83,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\blur2\fad(200,200)}藏起泪水不让人看见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:27.28,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\blur2\fad(200,200)}任凭随波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:32.04,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\blur2\fad(200,200)}抛却了掌控方向的桨
